  <steps>
    <step num="0">Set the nori sheet on a clean work surface. Season the rice with a pinch of salt. </step>
    <step num="1">Place half of the rice in the center of the nori and sprinkle with sesame seeds. Place the cooked salmon and shiso leaf on top. </step>
    <step num="2">Top with the remaining rice, then wrap the nori into a square and flip upside down. Let rest about 1 minute. </step>
    <step num="3">Cut in half. </step>
    <step num="4">Enjoy! </step>
  </steps>
